<b>Listing Name:</b><br>
<%= @reservation.listing.name %><br><br>
<b>Reservation Made By:</b><br>
<%= @reservation.user.email %><br><br>
<b>Reservation Price:</b><br>
RM <%= @reservation.listing.price %><br><br>
<b>Total Cost (After 6% GST):</b><br>
RM <%= @final_cost = @reservation.total_cost %><br><br>
